oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Implementing Expanded Services or Working Outside the Box
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Day, John D.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: veterinary practice
services
new services
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Practitioners are faced with several dilemmas when trying to expand their services. The first is making the decision to add to the current services offered, the second is making time to actually perform those services, and the third is getting compensated for the new services.
